description.en: Dogelon Classic (ELONC) is a premier dog-themed meme coin, built on the Ethereum Classic Network. With a focus on community, fun, and rewarding holders, Dogelon Classic brings the attractive features of its namesake, Dogelon Mars, from the Ethereum network to the Ethereum Classic network.
